{"1": {"Direccion": "18,212 followers, Here’s a short look at how we manufacture the bags for your Bag-in-Box®, assembling high-performance films, spouts, and taps into a compact and efficient solution.

What makes this packaging stand out?

✔️ It protects your product, keeping it fresh and safe thanks to the advanced multi-layer films and a reliable sealing system.

✔️ It helps reduce food waste by extending shelf life – and lowers packaging waste too, by using significantly less plastic than plastic bottles.

✔️ Compared to plastic or glass bottles, it enables lower carbon emissions across the supply chain.

✔️ Its compact shape and flexible format allow for optimized logistics: more volume transported with less space and weight.

It’s not just packaging, it’s a smarter way to protect products and reduce impact.#BaginBox#SmartPackaging#Sustainability#FoodPackaging#PackagingDesign#SmurfitWestrock"}, "2": {"Direccion": "18,212 followers, Consistency is key when serving millions of users worldwide. 🌎

That’s what the Vitop® Uno tap delivers every single day.

⚙️ From high-speed precision manufacturing to patented design, everything is made to ensure reliability at scale. 

And with a construction that allows for a future shift to mono-material, we’re also preparing for tomorrow’s recycling needs — without compromising performance.

Easy to use, precise, essential: Click and Drink! 

🎥 Take a closer look 👇#Vitop#BaginBox#Packaging#SmurfitWestrock#BagInBox#VitopUno"}, "3": {"Direccion": "18,212 followers, 🎉 1,000 days without accidents at our Bag-in-Box site in Pilar, near Buenos Aires, Argentina!

No capes, no superpowers… just a fantastic team, solid safety practices, and a lot of common sense 💪🦺

For 1,000 days, we’ve kept our site accident-free and that’s not luck, it’s the result of daily commitment and care for one another. 

Congratulations to the Baguin team — you’ve made safety a habit, and that’s something truly worth celebrating!

Let’s aim for 1,000 more 🚫🩹#SafetyFirst#BaginBox#SmurfitWestrock#ZeroAccidents#1KDays#Teamwork#BagInBox"}, "4": {"Direccion": "18,212 followers, The best wines have been recognized! 🌍🍷

The Best Wine in Box has come to a close, and the best wines have been awarded for their exceptional quality! 🏆✨

This prestigious competition featured wines from around the world, with each year seeing a remarkable improvement in the quality of entries.

It’s a true celebration of the potential of wines packaged in Bag-in-Box® offering not only convenience and sustainability but also premium wine quality. 🥂

A huge congratulations to all the winners and a big thank you to the organizers for making this event possible!#BestWineInBox#WineInnovation#BagInBox#WinePackaging#SustainableWine#WineLovers"}, "5": {"Direccion": "18,212 followers, 🍇 Discover the benefits of Bag-in-Box® withCollection Verre après Verre! 🍇

For over 20 years, Collection Verre après Verre has been offering premium wines using Bag-in-Box® packaging, which they have chosen for its convenience and sustainability.

Their wines, sourced from over 20 châteaux and estates in renowned regions such as Bordeaux, Côtes de Gascogne, the Loire Valley, and the South of France, are packaged directly at the wineries.

With 10+ red wine appellations, 4 rosé appellations, and 3 white appellations, Collection Verre après Verre brings top-quality wines to your glass. 

Proud to support them with our Bag-in-Box®! 🍷#BagInBox#PremiumWine#WineByTheGlass#SustainablePackaging#CollectionVerreAprèsVerre#WinePackaging"}, "6": {"Direccion": "18,212 followers, 💧 Roche Claire in Bag-in-Box®! 💚

Straight from the mountains, Roche Claire spring water comes in a Bag-in-Box®, a convenient packaging designed for the whole family, even the little ones!

By choosing Bag-in-Box®, Roche Claire reduces plastic use by up to 80% compared to their bottled format (1L and 1,5L), offering a more sustainable way to enjoy fresh, high-quality water.

A smart choice for your family and the planet! 🌍💙

Learn more about water in Bag-in-Box® :https://okt.to/7gkJeO#SustainablePackaging#BagInBox#PureWater#EcoFriendly#LessPlastic"}, "7": {"Direccion": "18,212 followers, 🚀 Vitop® Uno: millions produced, success that keeps growing! 🌍

Since its launch, Vitop® Uno tap has become a success, with millions of taps produced to meet increasing demand. What makes it preferred?

👉 Simplicity at its best: Vitop® Uno is designed for ease of use, making it the go-to solution for Bag-in-Box®.
 👉 A sustainable choice with reduced plastic waste without compromising on performance.
 👉 A legacy of trust: for over 30 years, Vitop® Original, the predecessor of Vitop® Uno, has been trusted by customers worldwide for its reliability and quality.#VitopUno#PackagingInnovation#Sustainability#BagInBox#CustomerSatisfaction"}, "8": {"Direccion": "18,212 followers, We had the pleasure of welcomingCiteoandAdelpheto our Epernay facility for a technical exchange on the future of Bag-in-Box® packaging. 🚀♻️

Alongside Pauline Tabourel, Orianne Broussard,Mehdi Besbes, and Valentin Fournel, we explored how eco-design can enhance separability and recyclability, making our packaging even more sustainable. 🌍💡

Great discussions, valuable insights, and a shared commitment to a circular economy. This is how we drive innovation in sustainable packaging!#SmurfitWestrock#Sustainability#Innovation#Packaging#Citeo#Adelphe#BagInBox#PouchUp#CircularEconomy"}, "9": {"Direccion": "18,212 followers, Liquid eggs in Bag-in-Box®! 💡🥚

As the liquid eggs market grows, choosing the right packaging solution is essential. 
Bag-in-Box® offers significant advantages for your industry:

✅ Specifically designed to meet the unique needs of liquid eggs.

✅ Available in sizes from 2L to 20L and 200L to 1000L for industrial use.

✅ Multi-layer films with a high oxygen barrier keep eggs fresh for longer.

Bag-in-Box® brings efficiency, sustainability, and quality to the liquid eggs industry. 🌱

Learn more:https://okt.to/eGDxOH#BagInBox#EggIndustry#LiquidEggs#PackagingInnovation#Sustainability"}, "10": {"Direccion": "18,212 followers, Eco-friendly packaging is not just a trend; it’s a must. 🌱

As consumers and businesses become more aware of their environmental impact, choosing sustainable packaging solutions is no longer optional, it’s essential.

With Bag-in-Box®, you can significantly reduce plastic consumption compared to other plastic packaging. 

Its lightweight design, optimized logistics, and high product-to-packaging ratio make it a smart choice for both the planet and your business.

♻️ Less plastic, less waste, more efficiency.
📦 A sustainable solution for a better future.

Let’s protect what matters, one box at a time!#Sustainability#BagInBox#LessPlastic#SmurfitWestrock#Water"}}

nombre: IMI B2B - Instituto de Marketing Industrial
resumen:
In IMI B2B we believe that a specific approach is necessary to address the characteristics and particularities of the Industrial / B2B (Business to Business) Marketing and Sales Strategy. We, therefore, founded an institute offering world-class knowledge and consulting for companies and associations. At the B2B Academy (www.imib2b.org/academia) it offers raining and teaching for executives and professionals in business and industries with marketing & sales responsibilities. IMI B2B organizes also events and meetings with specialists and has a club for companies and individuals to join, get part of the B2B community and participate in its development. 

IMI B2B has a strategic alliance with the prestigious Center for Business & Industrial Marketing, Georgia State University (Atlanta, USA), which ensures access and transfer of state-of-the-art know-how in its consultant services and teaching. At the moment, IMI B2B is present in Peru and Chile.

resumen:
En TalentXera, transformamos la manera en que las empresas conectan con el talento que necesitan para crecer y liderar en su industria. Somos más que un grupo de expertos en reclutamiento; somos socios estratégicos dedicados a encontrar a las personas clave que impulsarán el éxito de tu organización. Con más de 30 años de experiencia acumulada en la contratación de personal ejecutivo, gerencial y staff, hemos perfeccionado nuestra metodología para asegurar resultados excepcionales. Nuestro enfoque está diseñado para satisfacer las necesidades únicas de cada cliente, abarcando industrias diversas a lo largo de México, el Caribe y Centroamérica.  

Nos enorgullecemos de ser líderes en Reclutamiento Ejecutivo, brindando soluciones a medida para identificar, evaluar y contratar a los mejores candidatos para posiciones críticas dentro de tu empresa. Nuestra experiencia abarca desde roles estratégicos hasta posiciones altamente especializadas, siempre enfocándonos en garantizar una alineación perfecta entre el talento y los objetivos de tu organización. Además, en TalentXera somos pioneros en servicios de reclutamiento para Nearshoring, un modelo cada vez más relevante en el entorno global. Apoyamos a empresas que buscan establecer operaciones en México y América Latina, conectándolas con talento local que no solo cumple, sino que supera las expectativas. Entendemos las necesidades del mercado y la importancia de contar con personal capacitado para operar en un entorno globalizado, por lo que trabajamos de cerca con nuestros clientes para entregar resultados que generan impacto.  
En TalentXera, no solo encontramos candidatos, construimos equipos que transforman empresas. Cada proceso de reclutamiento se lleva a cabo con minuciosidad, garantizando que cada candidato no solo posea las competencias necesarias, sino que también comparta los valores y la visión de la organización.  
Si estás buscando un socio confiable, innovador y experimentado, en TalentXera estamos listos.

resumen:
Caban Condos Mexico is a privately owned & operated company that began in Saskatoon, Saskatchewan in 2010 under the parent company Regal Property Developments.

We operate in both Canada & Mexico specializing in custom home builds in Saskatchewan & Ocean Front Condo developments in Yucatan, Mexico. We are your trusted Canadian developer in south Mexico, with affordable ocean front prices. 

With our first project completed and sold out on the Caribbean sea in Mahahual, Mexico we are now beginning construction on a beautiful, luxurious 20 unit condomunium project in San Crisanto, Yucatan Mexico. Located just 45 minutes from the historic city of Merida, a population of 1 million people. In Merida you will find many amenities and services you are used to back home. Including Costco, Sam's Club, Starbucks, many high end shopping malls etc. Many airlines offer direct service to Merida, for Canadians WestJet now has seasonal direct flights from Toronto to Merida, and should be opening direct out of Calgary soon.

Prices starting at only $159,900 USD for 3 bedroom, 2 bath 1640 sq ft ocean front condos & $139,900 for ocean view beach villas. Penthouses feature private rooftop with own palapa bar, tv, and soaker pool. Beautiful white sand beaches and our infiniti pool will dazzle amaze you. Come find your paradise and escape here!

We are two guys from Saskatchewan, Canada building beautiful & affordable ocean front properties for you in paradise. 

Yours in paradise,

Mike Delaire & Parrish Kondra

resumen:
Somos un equipo de trabajo joven que ofrecemos nuestra colaboración para mejorar los indicadores de vuestras compañías. Nuestra experiencia en el mundo de la empresa privada durante más de 10 años nos respalda. 

No nos gusta describirnos como consultoría. Nos vemos como aliados estratégicos en el desarrollo de vuestros negocios. 

Podemos participar desde cuestiones muy generales como desarrollo organizacional, puesta en marcha de líneas productivas o desarrollo del sistema de gestión de calidad hasta cuestiones muy específicas como definir el proceso de fabricación de un tornillo estructural o mejorar la productividad de una línea de alambre galvanizado, por poner algún ejemplo. 

La metodología de trabajo es sencilla, partiendo de una reunión para conocer las necesidades y hacer una propuesta que se ajuste a lo solicitado. Nos adaptamos al cliente y necesitamos que haya una sinergia entre ambas partes para poder seguir adelante. Consideramos muy importante el feeling para que se cumpla el propósito. 

Estamos abiertos para todas aquellas organizaciones, privadas o públicas, con y sin ánimo de lucro, desde autónomos a grandes corporativos internacionales.

resumen:
En BRCO, somos pioneros en ofrecer soluciones avanzadas para centros de control, monitoreo, servicios cloud y conectividad M2M IoT. Diseñamos, implementamos y gestionamos entornos de trabajo ergonómicos y altamente funcionales, optimizados para mejorar la toma de decisiones y la gestión de crisis en tiempo real.

Nuestros Servicios:

Diseño de Centros de Control: Creamos espacios innovadores que facilitan un entorno de trabajo eficiente y ergonómico.

Centro de Control como Servicio (CRaaS): Proporcionamos monitoreo y control gestionado, permitiendo a nuestros clientes centrarse en sus operaciones.

Servicios Cloud: Ofrecemos soluciones cloud seguras y escalables para la gestión y almacenamiento de datos.

Conectividad M2M IoT: Facilitamos la comunicación entre dispositivos con soluciones de conectividad competitivas y eficientes.

Nos destacamos por nuestra capacidad de innovar y adaptarnos a las necesidades cambiantes del mercado, ofreciendo soporte local exclusivo y una implementación rápida y eficiente desde Perú. Nuestro compromiso con la excelencia y la satisfacción del cliente nos ha convertido en el socio preferido de organizaciones que buscan mejorar sus capacidades de monitoreo y respuesta.

resumen:
Gaia Therapy es el espacio online para tu bienestar holístico. El lugar para invertir en ti y cuidarte en todos los niveles.

Comprendemos la importancia de tus hábitos en este proceso y, por eso, hemos diseñado una variedad de cursos que abordan tus aspectos físicos, emocionales, mentales y espirituales. Elige el complemento que más resuene contigo y magnifica tu crecimiento personal.

Nuestra visión es motivarte a fortalecer tu equilibrio y nutrir tu bienestar en su totalidad, abarcando cuerpo, mente y alma. Estamos comprometidos en guiarte hacia un estado de bienestar integral, donde tu salud física y emocional se complementan y prosperan.

Descubre contenido que nutre tu alma a través de nuestros cursos, clases de yoga y meditaciones guiadas.

resumen:
RITMO is a cash flow management platform for e-commerce businesses in Europe and LATAM. RITMO’s all-in-one financial solution enables e-commerce to efficiently manage their cross-border payments and get access to flexible funding, making it easier for e-commerce entrepreneurs to spend time on building incredible businesses. 

Through this range of products, we are embedded in the day to day operations of our clients, offering financing for growth and enabling merchants to extend payment terms with suppliers.

RITMO was founded in 2021 by serial entrepreneurs and eCommerce veterans Raimundo Burguera, Iñaki Mediavilla, Iván Peña, and Prageet Sharma After our first year of operations, we have raised more than $225MM in financing and have active operations in five countries in Europe and Latin America.

resumen:
Somos la guía esencial en español para líderes visionarios.

Ofrecemos a nuestros lectores contenido de alto valor con rigor y veracidad sobre innovación y tendencias del mundo empresarial ayudándolos a mejorar la toma de decisiones en su vida cotidiana.

Siguiendo la línea de nuestra matriz en Estados Unidos (MIT SMR) exploramos cómo el liderazgo y la gestión se están transformando en un mundo disruptivo. 

Ayudamos a los líderes reflexivos a aprovechar las apasionantes oportunidades -y a enfrentarse a los retos- que surgen a medida que las fuerzas tecnológicas, sociales y medioambientales reconfiguran la forma en que las organizaciones operan, compiten y crean valor. 

Alentamos los comentarios, las preguntas y las sugerencias. Respetamos y apreciamos el punto de vista de nuestra audiencia; sin embargo, nos reservamos el derecho de eliminar o desactivar comentarios a discreción de nuestro moderador. 

Los comentarios que infrinjan nuestras directrices (véase más abajo) o utilicen un lenguaje que el personal de MIT SMR México considere abusivo, ofensivo, vulgar o de naturaleza intimidatoria serán eliminados inmediatamente. Los reincidentes podrán ser bloqueados indefinidamente. 

Directrices para comentarios en LinkedIn establecidos por nuestra matriz en Estados Unidos, MIT Sloan Management Review:

1. 1. Respeto. Los debates están muy bien, pero los ataques no. Cualquier comentario que cree un ambiente hostil será eliminado. 

2. 2. Discurso de odio. Los comentarios que contengan acoso, racismo, homofobia, sexismo o cualquier otra forma de incitación al odio serán eliminados.

3. 3. Lenguaje. Los mensajes vulgares pueden ofender a otros lectores y serán eliminados. 

4. 4. Datos personales. Cualquier comentario con información personal (dirección, número de teléfono, etc.) será eliminado.

resumen:
Colegio de Matemáticas Bourbaki es un espacio para el aprendizaje personalizado. Aquí se imparten métodos de enseñanza para acercar a las personas al trasfondo matemático en múltiples fenómenos y procesos. Nuestro objetivo es vincular la academia con aplicaciones de la realidad imperante.
 
La institución tiene una responsabilidad con la sociedad: procurar siempre el rigor académico en todos sus servicios. Su objetivo es convertir el conocimiento matemático en una inversión sostenible, que genere riqueza.
 

La especialización es la piedra central de la comprensión de los problemas, el primer paso en la ruta hacia las respuestas que demanda la realidad. La selección de material educativo asertivo y la atención a los detalles correctos aleja a Colegio Bourbaki de los cursos express. Asumimos que con claridad, constancia y transparencia, se construye un camino intelectual sincero.

resumen:
Estar informado en estos tiempos es bien difícil. 

- Estamos ocupados en nuestras vidas y la información disponible es demasiada, no hay tiempo para separar lo falso de lo real. Google y Facebook nos muestran sólo cosas parecidas a las que hicimos clic, no nos muestran cosas importantes.
- Los medios de siempre hablan rebuscado, seguirles el hilo es complicado.
- Los gobiernos o las empresas influyen para que se hable de lo que a ellos les interesa, no de lo importante.

Esta es nuestra razón de existir: ¡Ponerte al Día!

Nos ocupamos de informarte de las cosas importantes a tu alrededor, de forma sencilla y con pruebas, incluso de forma divertida. Explicamos lo que hay detrás de muchas cosas que ocurren. 

Los que quieren influir en lo que se habla son una voz, pero no la única
Queremos que estés al día ¡Rápido y bien!

Ahora Entiendo

resumen:
isEazy is a leading technology company specializing in e-learning solutions for corporate training, communication, and knowledge management. 

We offer a seamless, end-to-end training experience, providing all the tools organizations need to manage, design, and optimize their learning processes. 

Our team of experts is based across our offices in Spain, Mexico, Colombia, Brazil, and the United States, supported by a strong network of international partners. 

With over 22 years of experience and more than 10 million users, we have successfully delivered 100,000+ projects across 90+ countries for 1,000 clients worldwide. 

Thanks to our six proprietary e-learning tools, we make e-learning technology accessible to everyone: 

isEazy Author – A cloud-based authoring tool powered by AI to design and share e-learning content. 

isEazy Factory – A fast-track course design factory to create custom training in record time. 

isEazy Skills – The most comprehensive catalog to develop your team’s power skills. 

isEazy LMS – A next-generation, all-in-one online training platform. 

isEazy Engage – The go-to app for frontline workers. 

isEazy Game – A gamification app designed for corporate training. 

What are you waiting for? Join the new era of e-learning—AI made easy! 🚀

resumen:
■ We create, launch & support highly specialized travel brands that change the world for the better. ■

We are a global network of tourism experts, who create, launch and support highly specialized, individually branded travel services. All our services are led by passionate intrapreneurs with an extraordinary travel expertise.

■ Our Purpose ■

In the past, journeys were pulled from the catalogues of mass-marketed travel operators. But this is changing. More and more travellers prefer unique journeys that suit their taste, interests and budget. At the same time, they look for authentic and sustainable journeys that make a positive impact on both their own life and the communities they visit.

We believe that journeys like this can not be created “off-the-shelf”. Only passionate specialists will be able to organise unique, authentic and responsible trips.

This is why we encourage these passionate specialists to create their own brands - while we have their back. By adding a professional framework to their expertise we create reliable yet unforgettable travel experiences.

resumen:
Somos agente de carga, líder en Latinoamérica, contamos con 30 años de experiencia como integradores de servicios de flete internacional, marítimo, aéreo, terrestre y multimodal (combinación de cualquiera de los anteriores).
 
Tenemos 16 oficinas en México, Colombia, Perú, Costa Rica y Panamá. Ofrecemos las opciones más atractivas para importación y exportación de mercancías.

Nuestros principales objetivos son:

- Asesorarte en todo tu proceso logístico para que tu carga llegue segura de origen a destino final. (Puerta a puerta)
- Comunicación continua siempre por parte de un humano.
- Contamos con un equipo especializado, asignado para cada proyecto, el cual conocerás desde el primer contacto.
- Nos especializamos en minimizar los tiempos de tránsito y optimizar el presupuesto de tus embarques a través del análisis de la mejor propuesta para tus necesidades de carga.
- Nuestras principales rutas comerciales son: Colombia, Costa Rica, Perú, Panamá, Italia, España, Alemania y China.
- Las industrias en las que somos expertos son: Automotriz, Construcción, Perecederos, Industrial, Energética, Retail y Carga Proyecto (pesada y sobredimiensionada.

resumen:
We work one-on-one with teachers to create incredible educational tours that meet their specific needs and budget. All Explorica tours are fully inclusive and expertly designed to immerse participants in the local culture while introducing them to the people, places and experiences that make each destination unique.

Explorica is committed to enriching students through educational travel, and that means helping teachers extend the opportunity to as many students as possible. In addition to offering the guaranteed best prices in educational travel, we also provide scholarships, need-based financial assistance, and a variety of resources to ensure that every student is able to join their classmates on the trip of a lifetime.

Explorica is a part of WorldStrides, the global leader in educational travel and experiential learning. WorldStrides was founded in 1967 to provide middle school travel programs to Washington, D.C., and has grown to provide a wide range of programs for more than 550,000 students annually to over 100 countries around the world. WorldStrides offers experiential learning programs in educational travel, performing arts, language immersion, career exploration, service-learning, study abroad, and sports. Each of these experiences helps students to see beyond the classroom and to see the world – and themselves – in new ways. www.worldstrides.com

resumen:
En LAE International Education, creemos que la educación es la llave para un futuro prometedor y global. Nuestros valores fundamentales son el corazón de todo lo que hacemos:

🌟 Trayectoria y Experiencia: Más de 26 años de experiencia en el sector educativo nos avalan. Conocemos los entresijos de estudiar en el extranjero y sabemos cómo hacerlo realidad.

🤝 Servicio Personalizado: Entendemos que cada estudiante es único. Ofrecemos un servicio completamente personalizado para que encuentres la experiencia educativa perfecta que se adapte a tus sueños y metas.

📚 Amplia Oferta Educativa: Tenemos convenios con más de 800 instituciones y universidades a nivel mundial. Sea cual sea tu área de interés, tenemos la opción ideal para ti.

🌐 Cobertura y Respaldo Internacional: Más de 30 oficinas globales te brindan un apoyo constante, sin importar en qué rincón del mundo te encuentres.

🔍 Transparencia en Todo el Proceso: Creemos en la honestidad y la claridad. Te acompañaremos paso a paso, asegurándonos de que cada detalle de tu proceso sea transparente y claro.

💰 Servicio Gratuito: En LAE International Education, nuestro compromiso es ayudarte a alcanzar tus metas sin costos adicionales. No cobramos comisiones; el estudiante paga directamente a la institución o universidad en la que estudiará.

💥 Descuentos y Promociones Exclusivas: Tu futuro no debería ser costoso. Ofrecemos descuentos y promociones exclusivas para que puedas alcanzar tus objetivos educativos de manera asequible.

✅ Tasa de Aprobación de Visas del 98.5%: Nuestra tasa de aprobación de visas habla de nuestro compromiso con tu éxito. Hacemos que tu sueño de estudiar en el extranjero sea una realidad.

En LAE International Education, estamos dedicados a brindarte las mejores oportunidades educativas en todo el mundo. Únete a nuestra comunidad y descubre cómo podemos ser tu socio en la búsqueda de un futuro global. Tu educación, tu camino.

resumen:
For over 25 years, Globalsat Group has been at the forefront of mobile satellite services (MSS) across the Americas, serving a broad spectrum of industries including energy, government, defense, media, mining, finance, agriculture, NGOs, and tourism. Our solutions are designed to support mission-critical operations where seamless connectivity is essential.

We are driven by a commitment to leverage satellite technology for social and environmental impact. Our dedication has been recognized with the prestigious MSUA Satellite Mobility Innovation Award for two consecutive years, in 2023 and 2024.

Globalsat Group simplifies market access and logistics for our partners and clients across the Pan-American region. With a US distribution hub and a network of offices spanning the US, Argentina, Bolivia, Brazil, Central America & the Caribbean, Chile, Colombia, Ecuador, Mexico, and Peru, we ensure our customers receive reliable and effective support wherever they operate.

At the heart of Globalsat Group is a people-first philosophy. Our core values—trust, customer focus, and innovation—guide us in delivering superior service. This client-centered approach has not only garnered industry recognition, such as the "Top Land Mobility Satcom Innovation Award" and Frost & Sullivan's "Latin American Satellite Communications Company of the Year" on multiple occasions, but also the trust of our clients.

As we celebrate our 25th anniversary in 2024, we extend our heartfelt gratitude to our partners, colleagues, and customers who have been integral to our journey of innovation. Looking ahead, Globalsat Group remains committed to expanding our reach and delivering world-class satellite communication services to businesses and governments worldwide.

resumen:
The Mexican Electronics Telecommunications and Information Technologies Industries Chamber has more than 25 years in our country and is an entity representing the Electronics, Telecommunications and Information Tecnology Sector in Mexico, which promotes the development of said sector in a global environment with high quality services.

CANIETI is a public interest, autonomous institution with legal status and capital of its own, different from that of its members, established according to what is provided in the Act of Business Chambers and their Confederations.

Our main objective is to achieve the competitive development of the National Industry with a guild sense and social responsibility.

Individuals or corporations legally established both in the Mexican Republic and abroad, usually engaged in activities related to the electronics, telecommunications or informatics sectors, affiliate in CANIETI.

The Chamber is made up by more than 1000 member companies all over Mexico, gathered to defend and watch their rights and common interests. 

In 2003, 2004, 2006 and 2077 CANIETI received the National Prize of Ethics and Values awarded by the National Confederation of Industrial Chambers (CONCAMIN) to the body that shows commitment and social responsibility both for its members and the society in general.

History
- 1935  Association of Radio Distributors of Mexico City 
- 1940  Mexican Association of Radio Industrialists 
- 1945  Mexican Association of Radio and Television 
- 1950  National Association of the Electronics Industry  
- 1957  National Chamber of the Electronics and Electric Communications Industries. CANIECE 
- 1997  National Chamber of the Electronics, Telecommunications and Informatics Industry, CANIETI 
- 2007  Mexican Electronics Telecommunications and Information Technologies Industries Chamber, CANIETI.

resumen: Seso is a vertical software company for agriculture. resumen:
Say hello to Diatoms.

Microscopic plants called Diatoms absorb 10-20 billion tonnes of carbon dioxide (CO2) every year. That's equal to the amount of carbon captured annually by all of the world's rainforests.

Diatoms are considered the largest primary producers of oxygen on our planet. It is estimated that through photosynthesis, diatoms produce between 20% and 40% of the oxygen we breathe.

With the campaign "Keeping the Planet cool with Diatoms" we are trying to raise awareness about Diatom potential in CO2 removal.

We are in the process of removing 10GtCO2 by accelerating the growth of native diatoms in polluted open water systems.

resumen:
Classic has been a leader in supply chain solutions and shortage mitigation since 1985.  We keep your production lines running while protecting your supply chain.

We provide unrivaled flexibility and reliable material management solutions to many of the world’s largest electronics manufacturers and engineering companies.  We offer 14 global locations and regional distribution centers to serve your needs.  Led by our seasoned management team, Classic continues to set the industry standard through our robust supplier management and authentication protocols that yield unsurpassed supply chain security and protection.  Our focus is delivering fully traceable, quality products to all customers.

Our depth of expertise garnered from decades of service to countless OEMs and EMS companies, allows us to anticipate customer needs, predict trends, and navigate continued shifts in the global electronics marketplace.  Our financial strength and proprietary analytics enable customized services and products to meet specific customer requirements.  Classic’s considerable capabilities and commitment to service make us the independent distributor of choice for leading manufacturers of electronic products throughout the world.

resumen:
GreenStruxure, a partnership bringing together Schneider Electric’s industry leading expertise in renewable energy microgrids and Huck Capital’s sustainability-focused investments, launched in September 2020 to deliver modular, standardized Energy as a Service solutions to commercial, industrial and governmental medium-sized buildings in the U.S.

GreenStruxure is simplifying and accelerating the market adoption of renewable energy microgrids, offering an innovative outcome-based alternative for building owners and operators who want sustainable, cost-effective, resilient, onsite energy delivered to them hassle-free as a service with no upfront capital expenses or operational risks.

resumen:
From two-man job shops to high-volume production lines, manufacturing facilities have relied on JTEKT Machinery (formerly known as Toyoda Americas) for over 30 years. Our extensive lineup includes horizontal and vertical machining centers, bridge-type mills, grinding machines, and automation solutions. JTEKT machines are engineered for innovators, and built with the speed, strength, and capacity to get you there. 

We understand our success lies not only with our machines, but with our dedicated Engineering and Support departments. Whether it’s our ability to do high-speed and heavy-duty machining with ease, or because we repeatedly hit tight tolerances and time studies, JTEKT Machinery remains at the forefront of industry. Look no further to see the technology of tomorrow, because at JTEKT, that ingenuity begins here.

For more information regarding JTEKT Machinery's full lineup of machine tool solutions, visit our website (www.jtektmachinery.com) or reach out to our Support team by phone (800.257.2985) or email (service@jtektmachinery.com) today!

Learn about our employment opportunities by visiting our career website: https://www.toyoda.com/about-toyoda/careers

resumen:

Estamos comprometidos a ofrecer soluciones integrales para todos los sectores de la industria en Latinoamérica y el Caribe. 

Por más de 25 años, nos hemos posicionado como compañía líder en el mercado ofreciendo productos y servicios innovadores a nuestros clientes.

resumen:
Origen Tech is a US-based SAP consulting and products development firm focused on helping multinational companies (MNC’s) to successfully deploy SAP software in a true SaaS-based fashion, as the leading solutions provider for tax and reporting compliance as well as foreign trade process management for companies that run SAP in all the major economies in the region: USA, Brazil, Mexico, Colombia, Peru, Chile, Argentina, etc.

At Origen Tech, we integrate all aspects of cloud-enabled SAP solutions  for companies that have traditionally seen SAP as too expensive from a software license, deployment, and a sustainability perspective.

Through the adoption of cloud based intelligent enterprise software, state of the art AI technology and a solid repository of innovations combined with an agile approach, we empower organizations looking to scale. Origen Tech also support entrepreneurs, small and minority owned business who are looking for transformative ERP solutions to run their business on a modern and cloud-based platform. 

As a strategic systems integrator and application support specialist, we are uniquely positioned to handle the complex business environments of multinational corporations with specific expertise in LATAM & Brazil SAP localization projects, compliance, global trade, etc. We are distinguished as a “Best in Class” SAP partner providing comprehensive end-to-end SAP products, solutions, and consulting services from SMBs to Fortune 500 companies.

Origen’s culturally diverse team brings a practical hands-on approach to addressing complex business issues such as fiscal & statutory regulations and supply chain optimization with global, regional, and local consulting competencies. We help our clients achieve operational improvements by using a collaborative approach of aligning the IT strategy of the company with the goals of the business ensuring that our customers gain a competitive advantage in the marketplace with sustainable and compliant operations.

resumen:
You need a logistics and supply chain partner that can not only provide you with a good price, but a great value. Vector Global Logistics works with you to find efficient, cost-effective solutions for moving the products you care about from point A to point B. When you don’t have to worry about a successful arrival, you can focus on changing the world.

Vector provides world-class logistics services to make our partners and clients more successful while bettering the lives of everyone we come in contact with and creating a positive social impact. 

International and domestic shipping is provided through four key services:

-- Project logistics: Done-for-you planning and execution to streamline your complicated transportation needs

-- Non-profit expertise: Helping charities reach more people and improve more lives

-- Complex regions: Getting in and out of areas that other companies can’t and welcoming your challenges

-- Expedited services: Shipping products to destinations quickly to meet your deadlines and achieve your goals

How can we help you change the world?

www.VectorGL.com

resumen:
We make it possible for international student-athletes to combine college sports and higher education in the US and Canada. We connect international student-athletes with US and Canadian colleges and universities, offering game-changing college sports recruiting solutions for students, parents, coaches, and universities. 

Our team of 100+ full-time staff across 10 countries are, for the most part, former student-athletes. We know what it takes to go on the student-athlete journey with a scholarship, the challenges and opportunities before starting, during the college years, and after graduation. 

Together, we have developed an unmatched college coach network and have helped over 14,100 student-athletes over the years, from a wide variety of sports to more than 820 schools in all 50 US states and Canada. 

Our student-athletes typically receive a combination of sports scholarships, academic scholarships, and international scholarships. We have gained over 796 million USD in scholarships for our students, and have enabled and witnessed amazing, life-changing experiences while being part of their college journey. 

Keystone Sports is the sports division of Keystone Education Group. We have united Europe's most established international college sports recruiting agencies under one roof: 

AGM (Spain & LatAm)
CMAS (Mexico)
College Scholarships USA (Scandinavia + UK/Ireland/Australia/New Zealand)
Future Elite Sports (UK)
Sport-Scholarships (Germany, Austria, Switzerland)
Tennis Smart (UK & USA)
uniexperts (Germany, Austria, Switzerland)

We are proud of our legacy, and we are truly excited about the future of the college sports recruitment industry and the positive impact we’re creating through Keystone Sports. 

What's your journey?

nombre: ICAMI Centro de Formación y Perfeccionamiento Directivo
resumen:
ICAMI es el primer centro de formación y perfeccionamiento directivo de los directivos intermedios (gerentes, jefes y supervisores) de las empresas.

Durante el proceso de enseñanza, hacemos énfasis en la formación de la persona; al desarrollo del potencial profesional, ético y social de nuestros participantes a quienes se les faculta para el liderazgo, toma de decisiones y orientación al logro de resultados.

De esta forma ICAMI contribuye a generar valor para las organizaciones, desde hace más de 50 años.

resumen:
AGOL Worldwide is a time-critical logistics and Global Trade company specializing in the Aviation, Automotive, Information Technology, and Telecom industries.

We provide our clients with end-to-end supply chain and transportation solutions that ensure the timely and cost-effective delivery of their products and services.

Our Services

📦 Importer Of Record

AGOL Worldwide offers global IT and telecom companies a one-stop solution for their Importer of Record (IOR) needs, with white-glove delivery and import compliance certification services available in over 120 countries. We provide end-to-end solutions and exceptional service quality to ensure timely and efficient delivery of goods while complying with all relevant regulations.

🚚 On-board Courier

AGOL Worldwide's On-board Courier (OBC) service ensures safe and timely delivery of time-critical shipments, with a focus on reliability, speed, and transparency. Our experienced team provides end-to-end solutions and real-time tracking to meet the unique needs of businesses of all sizes.
 
⛓️ Supply Chain Solutions

AGOL Worldwide offers comprehensive and efficient Supply Chain Solutions as a third-party logistics provider. By leveraging our process-driven approach, we can plan and manage the entire supply chain process to meet the specific needs and requirements of our clients. This results in timely delivery of goods, improved supply chain management, and cost savings for our clients.

✅ 24/7 Dedicated Customer Service
✅ Expert Advice on 120+ Destinations
✅ 500+ Agents & Customs Brokers
